{"tid":2436841,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE日本線上騷　晒腿熱舞冧粉絲","createTime":"2021-03-07T12:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T14:35:25.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c91cbf4ffbb025ee6ca67072de77e164e54314c4","tid":2436841,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210307/photo/bkn-20210307105013466-0307_00862_001_01p.jpg?20210307105919\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210307105013466-0307_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20210307105919&h=c052a0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣成員周子瑜所屬的韓團TWICE受疫情影響，去年取消多場日本演唱會，並相隔1年於昨晚舉行日本線上演唱會「TWICE in Wonderland」，成員定延因為身體抱恙，僅參與部分演出。9位成員晒腿熱舞，除了獻唱去年推出的人氣歌《Fanfare》，又首度在日本騷上演繹《I CAN'T STOP ME》及《BETTER》等曲，日本成員Momo以日文跟粉絲打招呼，表示很高興可以闊別多時再跟粉絲一起盡興。她們在演唱會尾聲預告將會相隔半年，於5月12日推出第8張日語單曲《Kura Kura》，由老闆朴震榮作詞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210307/photo/bkn-20210307105013466-0307_00862_001_02p.jpg?20210307105919\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210307105013466-0307_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20210307105919&h=984c09d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210307/photo/bkn-20210307105013466-0307_00862_001_03p.jpg?20210307105919\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210307105013466-0307_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20210307105919&h=19696cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210307/photo/bkn-20210307105013466-0307_00862_001_04p.jpg?20210307105919\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210307105013466-0307_00862_001_04p.jp